OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781111161
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FBelow is a list of contact details for
OL,7,Furgent mental support in the North
OL,8,FEast region.
OL,10,FIf you feel like harming or hurting
OL,11,Fyourself or other people, you should
OL,12,Fcall 999 or go to your nearest
OL,13,FAccident and Emergency (A&E)
OL,14,Fdepartment.
OL,16,FFor non-emergency situations, you can
OL,17,Fvisit your GP or call NHS 111, where a
OL,18,Ftrained nurse can give you advice.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
