OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FIf you have a mental health problem
OL,7,Fand are experiencing a mental health
OL,8,Fcrisis, you can contact your local NHS
OL,9,FCrisis Resolution and Home Treatment
OL,10,FService:
OL,12,FGateshead - 0191 814 8899
OL,14,FHartlepool - 01429 285 858
OL,16,FMiddlesbrough - 01642 835 295
OL,18,FNorthumberland - 0303 123 1146
OL,20,FNewcastle - 0191 814 8899
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
