OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FThe following charities are also there
OL,7,Fto help.
OL,9,FMind have branches across the region
OL,10,Fproviding support for mental health
OL,11,Fsuch as talking therapies, counselling
OL,12,Fand crisis helplines.
OL,14,FLocal Mind numbers include:
OL,16,FTyneside and Northumberland - 0191 477
OL,17,F4545
OL,19,FWashington - 0191 417 8043
OL,21,FSunderland - 0191 5657218
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
