OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781111161
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FTeesside - 01642 257020
OL,8,FYou can find your local branch here.
OL,10,FMind's support line can be reached on
OL,11,F0300 102 1234.
OL,13,FThe charity can also signpost to
OL,14,Fresources for under 18s, and can
OL,15,Fprovide legal information and guidance
OL,16,Faround welfare and benefits.
OL,18,FIf U Care Share promotes emotional
OL,19,Fwellbeing in young people and supports
OL,20,Ffamilies affected by suicide. Call
OL,21,F0191 387 5661.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
