OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781111161
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FSamaritans provide confidential, non-
OL,7,Fjudgemental emotional support for
OL,8,Fpeople experiencing feelings of
OL,9,Fdistress or despair. Call 116 123
OL,10,F(freephone, landlines and mobile) or
OL,11,Femail jo@samaritans.org.
OL,13,FPAPYRUS is the national UK charity
OL,14,Fdedicated to the prevention of young
OL,15,Fsuicide. Call 0800 068 41 41 (Monday
OL,16,Fto Friday 10am-5pm and 7pm-10pm/
OL,17,Fweekends 2pm-5pm), text 07786 209697
OL,18,For email pat@papyrus-uk.org.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
