OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FCampaign Against Living Miserably
OL,7,F(CALM) provides a suicide prevention
OL,8,Fhelpline and online mental health
OL,9,Fresources for those who need them.
OL,10,FCall 0800 585858 (every day
OL,11,F5pm`midnight). A web chat service is
OL,12,Falso available.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
