CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781111161
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FA charity dedicated to improving
OL,7,Fmental health, reducing loneliness,
OL,8,Fand supporting wellbeing across
OL,9,FHartlepool. Including a focus on
OL,10,Findividuals who experience
OL,11,Fneurodiversity, including autism and
OL,12,FADHD, and who may find it more
OL,13,Fchallenging to access traditional
OL,14,Fmental health services. Call 01429
OL,15,F728040 or email office@lilyannes.co.uk.
OL,17,FRethink aims to make sure everyone
OL,18,Fseverely affected by mental illness
OL,19,Fhas a good quality of life. Call 0300
OL,20,F5000 927 (Monday to Friday 10am-2pm,
OL,21,Fnot including bank holidays).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
