OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781111161
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FSANE runs a national, out-of-hours
OL,7,Fmental health helpline offering
OL,8,Fspecialist emotional support and
OL,9,Finformation to anyone affected by
OL,10,Fmental illness, including family,
OL,11,Ffriends and Carers. Call 0300 304 7000
OL,12,F(every day 6pm-11pm).
OL,14,FStreetwise provides mental health
OL,15,Fsupport for young people. Call 0191
OL,16,F2305400 or 0191 2305533.
OL,18,FAnxiety UK runs a helpline on weekdays
OL,19,Fbetween 9.30am and 5.30pm. Call 03444
OL,20,F775 774.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
